<div class="empty-state">
  <h1>Create your first knowledge base</h1>
  <p class="text-muted">
    A knowledge base groups the documents Curator indexes for retrieval. Each
    KB has its own embedding model, retrieval strategy, and chat settings —
    one per use case (support, docs, internal wiki, …).
  </p>
  <div class="empty-state__actions">
    <%= link_to "Create your first knowledge base",
                new_knowledge_base_path,
                class: "btn btn--primary" %>
  </div>
</div>
